## 7. Event System

### 7.1 Cart Events
- `CartCreated`: Fired when a new cart is created
- `CartUpdated`: Fired when cart data is modified
- `CartDeleted`: Fired when a cart is soft deleted
- `CartRestored`: Fired when a soft deleted cart is restored

### 7.2 Item Events
- `ItemAdded`: Fired when an item is added to cart
- `ItemUpdated`: Fired when cart item is modified
- `ItemRemoved`: Fired when an item is removed from cart

